{"tid":1578272,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[渣馬online] 領取組隊任務","createTime":"2019-09-18T05:36:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T11:39:23.000Z","uid":282360,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ee2c74e0b96e10ad84317c6554e0e3ba0678fcaa","tid":1578272,"uid":282360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:36:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無論你有跑開定冇跑開都黎睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個係合家歡任務</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n渣打馬拉松今日開左公開組抽籤報名<br />\n10月6號截止 10月10號公佈結果<br />\n<br />\n當中10km可以用團隊制申請<br />\n<br />\n2至8人為一隊報名參賽 名額10,000個<br />\n<br />\n成功申請嘅隊名就會顯示係號碼布上面<br />\n<br />\n申請冇提及隊名嘅限制 不過唔知會唔會暗中DQ<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我地嘅任務就係 申請同運動有關嘅隊名</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果得幾隊同路人主辦方可以暗底DQ然後話抽籖結果Fail<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果有100隊同路人 全部都抽唔到 就推到渣馬唔解釋唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n＊留意返依家純粹apply係唔洗比錢嘅 <br />\n10號出左結果比錢先叫confirm<br />\n到時只要唔課金唔跑都唔緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n* 隊名唔可以重覆 如果隊名有人申請左個system會彈notification<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以改 建制A隊 建制B隊 如此類推<br />\n有創意有意思嘅名更歡迎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />傳送門呢度<a href=\"https://www.hkmarathon.com/zh-hant/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkmarathon.com%2Fzh-hant%2Findex.html&d=Ii72mHdDrz30Fn2z87Evjy3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=12925ba7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkmarathon.com/zh-hant/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Grxpjuc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGrxpjuc.jpg&h=559330a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"6f60213dccf70500e08c3aee7a0709605c9529f6","tid":1578272,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:37:10.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球響應「929全球集會抗赤納粹」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全世界一齊對準極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577380</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWqVmOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWqVmOV.jpg&h=075c7745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1tov9s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1tov9s.png&h=0af09f95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2195064f8853eb96ae71b1d4f5d87e0f70246899","tid":1578272,"uid":282360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:37:21.000Z","msg":"自推10下"},{"pid":"6a18890dcee7ac95f23cd60c3f9c0f599f9c5eea","tid":1578272,"uid":282360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:37:38.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"1b7f7c1aa0570b553c85c8546c966f39a08a9a1c","tid":1578272,"uid":282360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:37:50.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"cc957caaf261cd5fc2fc7dfb1958bc5843f92a7e","tid":1578272,"uid":282360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:38:55.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"a4985d7f43e7865013bf3e3da4e9736ab1b828be","tid":1578272,"uid":282360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:39:05.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"dd8c5791cac5b0c5d7920eaab32ee8fed6cddf16","tid":1578272,"uid":282360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score